{"tid":1599562,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一先港島後五區! 十月一先港島後五區!","createTime":"2019-09-28T04:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T17:49:38.000Z","uid":116526,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"01f1b07321f0de026b2cd20810f506b68276ff3a","tid":1599562,"uid":116526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:58:51.000Z","msg":"[傳貼]<br />\n<br />\n再次強烈呼籲！<br />\n十月一日，全民先港島，後五區！<br />\n大家要清楚，2百萬人，3百萬人，警方絕不放彈，若果和平慢行放彈，我地一定贏！不放彈，我地在國際線立即贏！<br />\n<br />\n所以！只要人數過百萬，我地一定贏！首先，一定！一定！一定！要到港島！<br />\n<br />\n百萬人行動在國際戰線成功後(國際各大傳媒看到後)，同一天入夜轉到五區再集會開花！<br />\n兄弟先爬上同一山頂(百萬港島)，晚後再各佔據點(五區開花)！<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆！不篤灰！不分化！不放棄！<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n因為堅持，才有希望！<br />\n願榮光歸香港🇭🇰！<br />\nWe are human!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n請再廣傳！"},{"pid":"b9a9fe828533096d743da9846d46624ac04d9820","tid":1599562,"uid":116526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"十月一先港島後五區!"},{"pid":"c0947ff7ec9a290034f5c453e2646ffc6c410b14","tid":1599562,"uid":220479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:59:53.000Z","msg":"推哂啲行動post上去呀<br />\n<br />\n［行動post] 做 乜 熱 門 冇 哂 行 動 post ？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599081</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6d4c0d3bdc46cfbae4700c65310df0e202e0b3a3","tid":1599562,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kPgiZuW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkPgiZuW.jpg&h=a3637093&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TKXYZuW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKXYZuW.jpg&h=43387bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDBbz3h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDBbz3h.jpg&h=a9642867&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4307aee3e2f5198bf577b13ee8d7c3e4033da905","tid":1599562,"uid":116526,